**Impact:** Struct is 48 bytes (1 `long` + 5 `double`) instead of 8 bytes. Every copy, parameter pass, array slot, and return value carries 6x overhead. With thousands of concurrent `DataSize` values in arrays/collections, this causes severe cache-line pressure.
